title: Best of The Program | Guest: Rep. Dan Crenshaw | 9/22/21
description:
Rep. Dan Crenshaw joins to talk about the ongoing crisis at the border. Are we headed toward a global government? The mayor of San Francisco had a poor excuse for being caught maskless, and Glenn and Stu make fun of the hypocrisy.
